#Pn Chomper

A browser game where the map is a Petri net. Tokens are chompers.
Transitions are doorways. Arcs are corridors.

The build hook bundles the assembled TypeScript into an inline script
and injects it into index.html, producing a self-contained dist/index.html
that runs in any browser with no server.

---

#Binding
    ~language typescript
    ~external index.html.tmpl
    ~on-build inject-bundle.ts
